{"tid":827099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【熱血公民】鄭松泰指控西九龍站玻璃窗嚴重損毀　明報實地照片：玻璃完好無缺","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T03:26:20.000Z","uid":163207,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d839f0bb7ebbc78f01645ef4291ace594cc364","tid":827099,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537284659766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537284659766&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3ada6f5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537284659766&h=ce02e810\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537284659766</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00001/44e615d7b20bb7fc69709feebc9d198d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F44e615d7b20bb7fc69709feebc9d198d.jpg&h=2736efa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風「山竹」周日（16日）襲港，本港多處樓宇玻璃爆裂。高鐵西九龍站採用超過4000塊玻璃組件建成玻璃天幕，亦被視為「高危」建築物。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰周二（18日）晚上，在facebook上載多幅網民提供的相片，指高鐵西九龍站在「山竹」吹襲下，天幕頂「天空走廊」有大量玻璃窗吹爆，其中底部一排玻璃窗大量損壞，「天空走廊」變成「露天走廊」。</span></strong>鄭質疑，是否設計問題及質量差劣所致，要求港鐵清楚交代西九龍站狀況。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人回覆本報查詢時表示，不清楚有關相片來源。港鐵指出，西九龍站天幕工程去年中大致完成，車站玻璃組件一直完好，在經歷近日超強颱風後，西九龍站天幕狀況正常，從無出現相中損毀情況。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本報記者晚上到西九龍站觀察，不見玻璃天幕爆裂。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥早上出席行會前，主動提及指高鐵西九龍站在經歷今次超強颱風的考驗後，「大體上是安然無恙」；但她表示，當然一定有少許或滲水問題，或有告示牌受損。"},{"pid":"df14fc756ffa635924b4f9ba84f0b94340384aab","tid":827099,"uid":34444,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/005020_4a4a05ad3ed0218500a5cf5cbfe99cd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F005020_4a4a05ad3ed0218500a5cf5cbfe99cd3.png&h=e423969c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fe0bd4c40cd9c13b7fb02df9b845fb5b6ca2e0e","tid":827099,"uid":163207,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00001/45083111bc30aff9d75a175b0608ce3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F45083111bc30aff9d75a175b0608ce3d.jpg&h=d3b78a46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39be02c9a32f1580d6d2939531bd73ea16b1dac1","tid":827099,"uid":34444,"like":6,"dislike":24,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"一個上面四塊窗 一個上面三塊窗 你當我白癡定弱智?"},{"pid":"e05408796cf91071e44140894272fa3d453d1174","tid":827099,"uid":163207,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"Cheng Chung Tai<br />\n4 hours ago<br />\n更新（22:55）<br />\n有記者朋友向港鐵查詢有關照片，港鐵回覆指「玻璃組件一直完好，狀況正常，從無出現照片中損毀情況。」<br />\n嗯，甘樣，不如聽日開放西九站俾傳媒及議員入去實地考察吧"},{"pid":"aea20d03d527e269cea47e5f62e9f5a7957f51c1","tid":827099,"uid":163207,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"39be02c9a32f1580d6d2939531bd73ea16b1dac1","tid":827099,"uid":34444,"like":6,"dislike":24,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"一個上面四塊窗 一個上面三塊窗 你當我白癡定弱智?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"你講乜呀Ching?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1863c4f38ebf48d89020a1f1a0bf9042be2e26","tid":827099,"uid":79307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e05408796cf91071e44140894272fa3d453d1174","tid":827099,"uid":163207,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"Cheng Chung Tai<br />\n4 hours ago<br />\n更新（22:55）<br />\n有記者朋友向港鐵查詢有關照片，港鐵回覆指「玻璃組件一直完好，狀況正常，從無出現照片中損毀情況。」<br 